#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/catalog.ex:200
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Escape Union City and uncover your past in this cyberpunk classic by Revolution Software. One of the greatest point & click adventures ever made."
msgstr "脱逃联合城 揭开你在这篇革命软件的 网络朋克经典中的过去 点击冒险史上最伟大的点之一( C)."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/rekkr.ex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Every asset is lovingly hand-crafted — from the beautifully detailed environments (frozen fjords, ruined villages, underground caverns) to the unique weapon set including axes, bows, and runic magic. The art style is distinctly its own while honoring the DOOM engine's capabilities."
msgstr "每一个资产都是有爱心的手工制作的——从美丽细腻的环境(冰冻的峡湾,被毁的村庄,地下洞穴),到包括斧头,弓形,和野兽魔法在内的独特武器集. 艺术风格在尊重DOOM引擎能力的同时,明显属于自己的风格."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_bass.ex:24
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Examine / open verb menu"
msgstr "检查/ 打开动词菜单"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_drascula.ex:24
#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_dreamweb.ex:24
#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_fotaq.ex:24
#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/scummvm_soltys.ex:24
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Examine object"
msgstr "检查对象"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/chex_quest.ex:40
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Explore every corner — the levels have hidden areas with extra Zorch ammo."
msgstr "探索每一个角落——关卡有隐藏区域,并有额外的佐奇弹药."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/arcade/content/librequake.ex:45
